t-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;margin:0;padding:0"><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="max-width:600px;margin:0 auto"><tbody><tr style="width:100%"><td style="padding:32px"><div style="border-bottom:1px solid #e4e4e7;padding-bottom:24px;margin-bottom:32px"><span style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#18181b;letter-spacing:-0.5px">Acme</span></div><h1 style="font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:#09090b;line-height:1.3;margin:0 0 16px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif">New sign-in detected</h1><p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#09090b;margin:0 0 16px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif">Hi Marie Dupont,</p><p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#09090b;margin:0 0 16px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif">A new sign-in was detected on your Acme account. If this was you, there&#x27;s nothing to do. Otherwise, secure your account right away.</p><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="background:#f4f4f5;border-radius:8px;margin:24px 0"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:20px"><p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#09090b;margin:0 0 16px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif"><strong>Date and time<!-- --> :</strong> <!-- -->Friday, January 2, 2026 at 3:04 PM<!-- --> (UTC)</p><p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:#09090b;margin:0 0 16px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif"><strong>IP address<!-- --> :</strong> <!-- -->203.0.113.42</p><p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:#71717a;margin:0 0 16px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif"><strong>Device<!-- --> :</strong> <!-- -->Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10_15_7) Chrome/125.0</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table width="100%" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="margin:24px 0"><tbody><tr><td align="center"><a href="https://example.com/dashboard/security" style="color:#ffffff;text-decoration-line:none;display:inline-block;background-color:#6366f1;text-decoration:none;padding:12px 32px;border-radius:8px;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;line-height:1.5;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif" target="_blank">Review my active sessions</a></td></tr></tbody></table><hr style="width:100%;border:none;border-color:#e4e4e7;border-top:1px solid #eaeaea;margin:24px 0"/><p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:#71717a;margin:0 0 16px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif">If you don&#x27;t recognize this sign-in, change your password and contact support. In an emergency, sign out of all sessions from your account&#x27;s security page.</p><div style="border-top:1px solid #e4e4e7;padding-top:24px;margin-top:48px;text-align:center"><p style="font-size:12px;color:#71717a;margin:0 0 8px">You&#x27;re receiving this email because you have an account on Acme.</p><p style="font-size:12px;color:#71717a;margin:0">© YYYY Acme. All rights reserved.</p></div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table><!--/$--></body></html>"`;

